00:00:41.107 --> 00:00:44.410
I<i> can</i> afford lamp shades.

00:00:44.443 --> 00:00:47.346
You know what,
let's take the focus off of me

00:00:47.379 --> 00:00:50.283
and put it on the everyman
doing good

00:00:50.316 --> 00:00:51.684
in my long-running,

00:00:51.717 --> 00:00:54.187
