00:04:13.485 --> 00:04:16.088
Some real Super Ballet-Dad shit.

00:04:16.121 --> 00:04:18.691
-(sweet music plays)
-Ah, yeah. See?

00:04:18.724 --> 00:04:20.593
You are not better than me.

00:04:20.626 --> 00:04:22.662
Shove this up
your Facebook feed.

00:04:22.695 --> 00:04:25.131
You know what? Puppy me.
(bleep) it.

00:04:25.164 --> 00:04:27.400
Yeah. Oh.

00:04:27.433 --> 00:04:29.402
(cheering and applause)

00:04:29.435 --> 00:04:31.704
Did you have a dog? Yeah?

00:04:31.737 --> 00:04:34.073
Who's your Superdad now, bitch?

00:04:34.106 --> 00:04:36.809
As a matter of fact,
bring on the summer interns.

00:04:36.842 --> 00:04:40.146
Ah, yeah. See, this is easy.

00:04:40.179 --> 00:04:42.682
I could do this all day.

00:04:42.715 --> 00:04:45.418
Dance with me, kids,
dance with me.

00:04:45.451 --> 00:04:46.986
Dance with me.

00:04:47.019 --> 00:04:48.754
My kids love me, too.

00:04:48.787 --> 00:04:50.056
No one's better than me.

00:04:50.089 --> 00:04:51.257
I'm the Superdad.

